list_definition_mean.definitions_word_en: (of a person or animal) have severe difficulty in breathing because of a constricted or obstructed throat or a lack of air.
list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_en: Willie choked on a mouthful of soda
list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_vn: Willie nghẹn ngào trên một ngụm soda

list_definition_mean.definitions_word_en: fill (a passage or space), especially so as to make movement difficult or impossible.
list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_en: the roads were choked with traffic
list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_vn: Những con đường bị nghẹn với giao thông

list_definition_mean.definitions_word_en: make (someone) speechless with a strong feeling or emotion.
list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_vn: Anh ta bị nghẹn giận dữ

list_definition_mean.definitions_word_en: enrich the fuel mixture in (a gasoline engine) by reducing the intake of air.
list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_en: carbon monoxide results during a cold start, when an engine is choked
list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_vn: Kết quả carbon monoxide trong một khởi đầu lạnh, khi một động cơ bị nghẹn

list_definition_mean.definitions_word_en: a valve in the carburetor of a gasoline engine that is used to reduce the amount of air in the fuel mixture when the engine is started.
a sound produced by a person or animal having difficulty in breathing.
list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_vn: một chút sặc của tiếng cười

list_definition_mean.definitions_word_en: the inedible mass of silky fibers at the center of a globe artichoke.
